  "detailed_description": "Scrolls of the lord is a game in the setting of a fantasy world that has survived its end. You play as a knight brought back to life as a \"Devastated\". A mysterious entity that has given you back your mind asks you to do something for it and you can't refuse.<br><br><strong>Combat system</strong><br>Use weapon blocking and fast or slow strikes depending on the situation.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/723070/extras/c556d28339d052cbd2724e0410d7d27b.poster.avif?t=1742312507\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/723070/extras/c556d28339d052cbd2724e0410d7d27b.webm?t=1742312507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/723070/extras/c556d28339d052cbd2724e0410d7d27b.mp4?t=1742312507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Magic</strong><br>Use magic spells if you prefer ranged combat.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/723070/extras/4cbffce9c7d5f842ceb7632e17d039f0.poster.avif?t=1742312507\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/723070/extras/4cbffce9c7d5f842ceb7632e17d039f0.webm?t=1742312507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/723070/extras/4cbffce9c7d5f842ceb7632e17d039f0.mp4?t=1742312507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
